Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Big cars are back
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407h69
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Jun 1977
US drivers want big-car status despite fuel fears. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.